IRUNGA Longin

IRUNGA  Longin  yavutse mu 1972 avukira  mu mujyi wa Rubumbashi muri Repubulika iharanira Demokarasi ya Kongo, aracyari ingaragu  nyuma yo kurangiza  amashuri yisumbuye muri Electricite Industriere  ntiyabashije gukomeza  kaminuza .
Yatangiye  gukina film muri 2008 akaba amaze gukina filime nyinshi harimo   Igitambo, Agaca, Nd’umukirisitu, Serwakira, Rurahiye, Ubwungo Series, Karani Ngufu,  n’izindi  yagiye agaragaramo.

